12-30 March 2007 
</p>
<p><b>REPORT TO THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY ON THE FOURTH SESSION 
OF THE HUMAN RIGHTS COUNCIL</b>*<b> 
</b></p>
<p><b>Vice-President and Rapporteur:  Mr. Musa Burayzat (Jordan) 
Draft report of the Council</b>**<b> 
</b></p>
<p>                                                 
</p>
<p>  *<b>  </b>The format of the present report is based on the agenda and &#8220;Draft framework for a 
programme of work of the Human Rights Council for the first year&#8221; for the fourth session as 
adopted by the Council in its decisions 1/105 of 30 June 2006 and 2/103 of 6 October 2006. It 
should therefore not serve as a precedent for future sessions of the Council. 
</p>
<p>**<b>  </b>Document A/HRC/4/L.10 contains the chapters of the report relating to the organization of 
the session and the items on the agenda. Resolutions and decisions adopted by the Council are 
contained in document A/HRC/4/L.11. </p>

