questions and made their concluding remarks. 
</p>
<p>64. At the 17th meeting, on the same day, statements in exercise of the right of reply were 
made by the representatives of Algeria, Sri Lanka and Ukraine. At the 18th meeting, on </p>

 <p> 
</p>
<p>22 March 2007, a statement in exercise of the right of reply was made by the representative of 
