</b></p>
<p><i>Follow-up to resolution S-1/1 
</i></p>
<p>101. At the 19th meeting, on 22 March 2007, Mr. John Dugard, Special Rapporteur on the 
situation of human rights in the Palestinian territories occupied since 1967, presented his report 
(A/HRC/4/17). He also presented his report (A/HRC/4/116) pursuant to resolution S-1/1 entitled 
&#8220;Situation of human rights in the occupied Palestinian territory&#8221; (see also paragraph 46 above). 
The observers for Israel and Palestine made statements, as concerned countries, or parties. 
</p>
