Germany (on behalf of the European Union), Mexico, the Netherlands and Pakistan (on behalf of 
the Organization of the Islamic Conference); 
</p>
<p> (<i>b</i>) Observers for the following States: Italy, Luxembourg, Singapore, Slovenia, Sweden 
and the United States of America; </p>

 <p> 
